Fast Path
- Updates and Removes Call CAS or RCU over the Bucket (Cas for fastest Inlined Operion, RCU for Larger MVCC type operation on larger Values liek maps)

Slow Path
- Spin Lock For Rehashing

use a atomic u32 for the state machine
- MSB = 1 means we are rehashing, if MSB = 0 then we are free to CAS or RCU
 31 bit is a control bit
 30-0 are the Count of threads/operations (ref count)



